Good evening Rachel, thank you for your previous email with the estimate for the replacement of the cvt unit on Shannon's Rogue. Fortunately the customer's contract covers the replacement of the transmission assembly. Due to the costs, we will be approving the replacement with a used unit as you quoted. Please be advised, the customer is responsible for any diagnostic fees, fluids, filters, environmental fees, and the alignment, as well as a $100 deductible. Our Mitchell Labour Guide lists the transmission replacement labour as 14.3 hours, so we will be proceeding with this allocated labour time for the repair.  Additionally, our maximum hourly rate for labour is $130/h. If you choose to charge above this amount, the customer will be responsible for the difference. The payout is as follows:

Parts-$2105.95
Labour-$1859.00 (14.3 hours x $130/h)
Deductible-$100
Gst-$198.25
Pst-$130.13
Authorization-KNRX9KLUXZ

Matthew Puls
